## Data Flow Description

| Step | Flow | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| 1 | User → Auth | User signs in via Google |
| 2a | User → P1 | User adds/edits receipt or warranty |
| 2b | User → P2 | User views/filters items list |
| 2c | User → P3 | User requests to delete item |
| 2d | User → P4 | User triggers manual sync |
| 2e | User → P5 | User schedules a reminder |
| 2f | User → P6 | User exports data to CSV |
| 3a | VM → DS1 | Save item to local Room DB |
| 3b | DS1 → VM | Query items from Room DB |
| 3c | VM → DS1 | Delete from Room DB |
| 4a | P1 → DRIVE | Upload image to Google Drive |
| 4b | P1 → FIREBASE | Upload item data to Firestore |
| 5a | P3 → FIREBASE | Delete from Firestore |
| 5b | P3 → DRIVE | Delete image from Drive |
| 6a | P4 → FIREBASE | Full sync with Firestore |
| 6b | P4 → DRIVE | Upload/download images |
| 6c | P4 ↔ DS1 | Merge cloud/local data (timestamp-based) |
| 7 | P5 → WORK | Schedule WorkManager reminder |
| 8 | WORK → USER | Notification triggered to user |
| 9 | P6 → USER | Export data to CSV file |
